snippet.title: Shadow and Bone: Enter The Fold | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Return to the Grishaverse with SHADOW AND BONE: Enter The Fold, a new mobile game (set between Seasons 1 and 2) that you can DOWNLOAD NOW exclusive on Netflix Mobile #GeekedWeek

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 247 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Shadow and Bone: Enter The Fold | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Shape the fate of the Grishaverse. Travel war-torn Ravka and decide which powers prevail in this interactive adventure based on the fantasy series.
